                      "fill": "#706860",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "CLI for daily developer use. Secrets encrypted with Argon2id + AES-256-GCM. Environment profiles with inline secret resolution ($secret:NAME). SSH key management. Reference sources for study. Everything local. Zero external services.",
